a, b = map(str, sys.stdin.readline().split())
slicer, checker = len(a), len(b) - len(a) + 1

tmp_min = 99999
for i in range(checker):
    count = 0
    tmp_b = b[i:i+slicer]
    for j in range(slicer):
        if a[j] != tmp_b[j]:
            count += 1
    tmp_min = min(tmp_min, count)
print(tmp_min)
